            <p>With over two decades of experience creating extensive internet systems, Suffix E Solutions is a top provider of networking and software services... (full text from image)</p>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus/iso1.png" width="80" />
                <img src="~/images/aboutus/iso2.png" width="80" />
                <img src="~/images/aboutus/iso3.png" width="80" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-right text-center">
            <img src="~/images/about/team.gif" alt="Team GIF" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;" />
            <div class="stats-box mt-3">
                <p><strong>15000+</strong> Students are Placed</p>
                <p><strong>500+</strong> Partner Companies</p>
                <p><strong>100%</strong> Placement Assistance</p>
